# Movie Rating Tool

A simple Python package to manage your personal movie ratings, compare them with online ratings, see statistics and beautiful charts.

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/nasimabhari/movie-rating-tool.git
cd movie-rating-tool
uv pip install -e .
uv run -m movie_rating_tool
```
